<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4632185>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Chaetodellus spp., females. (A–F). Chaetodellus comatus sp. nov. (A) Dorsal shield; (B) ventral idiosoma; (C) sternal shield, anterior portion; (D) epistome; (E) tarsus II, distal section; (F) tubes of sperm access system opened onto coxae III. (G) Chaetodellus meganalis, dorsal shield. Scale bars: 100 µm (A, B, F, G), 50 µm (C, D) and 25 µm (E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4632185/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

